# 🎂 Personalized Birthday Calendar

An interactive and aesthetic web application that highlights a user's birthday in the current year's calendar.

## ✨ Features
- 📅 Dynamic calendar generation
- ❤️ Highlights selected birthday
- 💬 Displays personalized quote
- 🎨 Elegant UI with animations
- 📱 Responsive design

## 🚀 Live Demo
 https://kavyadasariraju.github.io/birthday-highlight-calendar/

## 🛠️ Tech Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

## 💡 Idea
This project focuses on combining UI design with logic to create a personalized and engaging user experience.

